posting_body: ['Welcome to Stoneleigh at the Reserve', 'Rental Information', 'Pricing:', '$1685 - $1795/Month | 1 Bedroom 1 Bath | 1016', 'sq ft', 'Lease Term:', 'Variable', 'show contact info', 'Apartment Amenities', '− Air Conditioning', '− Built-In Office/Desk', 'In Select Units', '− Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '− Garbage Disposal', '− Linen Closet', '− Microwave', '− Pantry In Select Units', '− Patio/Balcony', 'In Select Units', '− Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '− Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'Community Features', '− Bike Storage', '− Car Wash Bay', '− Elevator', '− Fitness Center', '− Free Weights', '− Gameroom', '− Picnic Area', '− Pool', '− Recycling', '− Resident Lounge', '− Barbecue/Grill Area', '− Basketball Half-Court', '− Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '− Controlled Access Building', '− Disposal Chutes', '− On-site Maintenance & Management', '− Planned Social Activities', '− Racquetball Court', '− Reserveable Clubhouse', '− Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'About Community', 'Description:', 'Some apartment complexes can come off as cold and impersonal... not Stoneleigh at the Reserve found in Plymouth, Minnesota.', "Our traditional elegance is evident from our coffered ceilings to our stately gables; from the minute you step onto our property, you can't help but feel like you're home.", 'Come find out why 94% of our residents would recommend our community to a friend!', 'Location:', '5200 Annapolis Ln N', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Sun: 12:00 PM - 4:00 PM', 'Additional Information', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Our Management Company:', 'Weidner Apartment Homes, LLC', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '8A59AE630F1F447']
